[SN]TITLE[SN]
'Accept deal' to end Arriva Trains Wales dispute

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Leaders of the train drivers' union have urged acceptance of a deal which would end a dispute over pay and conditions at Arriva Trains Wales.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The executive of Aslef said industrial action has been suspended until a ballot of members is known.
It is recommending that a revised package offered by the company is accepted.
The drivers have taken strike action in the row over pay and conditions, such as the length of shifts.
